@startuml sd_ReportService_getTaxReport
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title ReportService.getTaxReport(yearMonth) - 个税申报表

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "ReportController" as Ctrl
participant "ReportService" as RptSvc
participant "SalaryRecordRepository" as RecRepo
participant "Employee\n(实体)" as Emp

Client -> Ctrl: GET /api/reports/tax-report?yearMonth=202403
Ctrl -> RptSvc: getTaxReport(yearMonth)
RptSvc -> RecRepo: findByYearMonth(yearMonth)
RecRepo --> RptSvc: List<SalaryRecord>
note right of RptSvc #F0F8FF
  **构建申报行(stream):**
  每个记录 → LinkedHashMap:
  "姓名" → employee.name
  "身份证号" → employee.idCard
  "工资号" → employee.employeeNo
  "累计收入" → cumulativeIncome
  "累计专项扣除" → cumulativeDeduction
  "累计已缴税额" → cumulativeTaxPaid
  "本月应纳税额" → incomeTax
  "实发工资" → netPay
end note
RptSvc --> Ctrl: List<Map<String, Object>>
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse → JSON\n[ {姓名, 身份证号, 累计收入, ...} ]

@enduml
